# Vari√°veis de ambiente
# @baseUrl = https://staging.storage.pe.gov.br
@baseUrl = http://localhost
@apiKey = your_api_key_here

### -----------------------------------------
### Criar bucket
### -----------------------------------------
PUT {{baseUrl}}/meu-bucket-teste
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
x-amz-acl: private

### -----------------------------------------
### Listar buckets
### -----------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### -----------------------------------------
### Upload de arquivo para o bucket
### -----------------------------------------
PUT {{baseUrl}}/meu-bucket-teste/teste.pdf
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./teste.pdf

### -----------------------------------------
### Listar objetos no bucket
### -----------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/meu-bucket-teste
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### -----------------------------------------
### Baixar o arquivo
### -----------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/meu-bucket-teste/teste.pdf
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}